mily:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ly the work</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> of Select Committees, in the final year before that election.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">The </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">most </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">obvious</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> benefit of </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">fixing the date of the General Election</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> for Select Committees is that</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">it </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">enables Committees </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">to “programme” their inquiries </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">during the final year of the Parliament.  In previous Parliaments, </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the uncertainty over the date of Dissolution would affect a Committee</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">in a long-term or a particularly </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">detailed inquiry; the danger would be that, once the PM had announced the General Election, Committees would either have to hurriedly  curtail an inquiry and rush out its Report, with the result that that Report was not as complete</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">as the Committee might otherwise wish, or otherwise abandon the inquiry without producing a Report, with the hope that its successor Committee would take up the matter in the new Parliament.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">I hope that these brief comments are helpful.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">15 January 2014</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>